@node installazione "Installation"

        MiraNAVIGATOR needs:

          1 - MUI 3.0 (or above)

          2 - The comand "MultiView" must be placed in the
              path "SYS:Utilities/MultiView".

          3 - The programs "Extractor","List" and "Sort"
              in "C:" or another search path.

